SIMPLE: moonstruck
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Moonstruck
<hw>Moon"struck`</hw> <pr>(m⟦oomac⟧n"str⟦ucr⟧k`)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>Mentally affected or deranged by the supposed influence
of the moon; lunatic.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Produced by the supposed influence of the
moon.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Moonstruck</xex> madness.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Made sick by the supposed influence of the moon, as
a human being; made unsuitable for food, as fishes, by such supposed
influence.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>moonwalk</ent>⟦br⟧
